messages.subject: Re: [samuraihistory] Which character from "the last samurai" are you?
messages.msgSnippet: I got rated as 1. Date Masamune 2. Oda Nobunaga 3. Toyotomi Hideyoshi A little strange because I always portrayed myself as Shingen. I wish you all good
messages.messageBody:
I got rated as
1. Date Masamune
2. Oda Nobunaga
3. Toyotomi Hideyoshi

A little strange because I always portrayed myself as
Shingen.

I wish you all good holidays. I also hope that I can
have a chance to meet some of you in the future once I
am well established in America.



Sincerely,





Changsub Lee
